README - libbpm examples
************************


data/         -- contains some datafiles for the examples
wfprocess.c   -- simple libbpm based waveform processing program
libbpm-test.c -- some testing routines

c-project/    -- example C project with Makefile using libbpm

root-project/ -- example C++ project marrying ROOT and libbpm, just
                 generates a waveform, DDC's it and spits the
		 generated amplitudes, phases and reconstructed ones
		 into a tree
